<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="12" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,1023,1266]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1060,1086]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Bernardo, U. &amp; Gebiola, M. &amp; Xiao, Z. &amp; Zhu, C. - D. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J. &amp; Viggiani, G." box="[324,578,1059,1086]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="437 - 446" refId="ref42594" refString="Bernardo, U., Gebiola, M., Xiao, Z., Zhu, C. - D., Pujade-Villar, J. &amp; Viggiani, G. (2013) Description of Synergus castaneus n. sp. (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Synergini) associated with an unknown gall on Castanea spp. (Fagaceae) in China. Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 106 (4), 437 - 446. https: // doi. org / 10.1603 / AN 13009" type="journal article" year="2013">
Bernardo 
<emphasis box="[437,487,1059,1085]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">et al</emphasis>
. (2013)
</bibRefCitation>
described an oak cynipid inquiline, 
<taxonomicName authority="Pujade-Villar, Bernardo &amp; Viggiani, 2013" authorityName="Pujade-Villar, Bernardo &amp; Viggiani" authorityYear="2013" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Synergus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="castaneus">
<emphasis box="[994,1214,1060,1086]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Synergus castaneus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Pujade-Villar, J. &amp; Equihua-Martinez, A. &amp; Estrada-Venegas, E. G. &amp; Melika, G." pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="209 - 218" refId="ref50222" refString="Pujade-Villar, J., Equihua-Martinez, A., Estrada-Venegas, E. G. &amp; Melika, G. (2013) A new genus of oak gallwasp, Kokkocynips Pujade-Villar &amp; Melika gen. n., with a description of a new species from Mexico (Hymenoptera, Cynipidae). Acta Zoologica Mexicana, Nueva Serie, 29 (1), 209 - 218. https: // doi. org / 10.21829 / azm. 2013.291396" type="journal article" year="2013">Pujade-Villar, Bernardo &amp; Viggiani, 2013</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, from 
<collectingRegion box="[490,669,1095,1121]" country="China" name="Anhui" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Anhui Province</collectingRegion>
, which was suspected to be a gall-inducer. Some years later, the true gall-inducer of the gall, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pujade-Villar, Wang &amp; Guo" authorityYear="2018" box="[421,524,1131,1158]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Andricus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="henryi">
<emphasis box="[421,524,1131,1158]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">A. henryi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, was described from 
<collectingRegion box="[764,864,1131,1157]" country="China" name="Zhejiang" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Zhejiang</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Pujade-Villar, J. &amp; Guo, R. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Ferrer-Suay, M." box="[878,1174,1131,1158]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="131 - 139" refId="ref50418" refString="Pujade-Villar, J., Guo, R., Wang, Y. &amp; Ferrer-Suay, M. (2018 b) First record of an Andricus chestnut gall wasp from the Oriental Region: a new species from China (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini). Entomotaxonomia, 40 (2), 131 - 139." type="journal article" year="2018">
Pujade-Villar 
<emphasis box="[1036,1085,1131,1157]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">et al</emphasis>
. 2018b
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="12" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,1023,1266]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,295,1167,1193]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Biology.</emphasis>
Only females, probably of the sexual generation, have been described. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pujade-Villar, Wang &amp; Guo" authorityYear="2018" box="[1104,1284,1167,1193]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Andricus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="henryi">
<emphasis box="[1104,1284,1167,1193]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Andricus henryi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
induces integral twig galls on 
<taxonomicName box="[353,459,1204,1230]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Castanea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[353,459,1204,1230]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Castanea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Table 1; 
<bibRefCitation author="Pujade-Villar, J. &amp; Guo, R. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Ferrer-Suay, M." box="[573,863,1203,1230]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="131 - 139" refId="ref50418" refString="Pujade-Villar, J., Guo, R., Wang, Y. &amp; Ferrer-Suay, M. (2018 b) First record of an Andricus chestnut gall wasp from the Oriental Region: a new species from China (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini). Entomotaxonomia, 40 (2), 131 - 139." type="journal article" year="2018">
Pujade-Villar 
<emphasis box="[729,778,1203,1229]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">et al</emphasis>
. 2018b
</bibRefCitation>
). This is the only 
<taxonomicName box="[1065,1254,1203,1229]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis box="[1065,1166,1203,1229]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Andricus</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
globally known to gall 
<emphasis box="[229,342,1240,1266]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
<taxonomicName box="[229,338,1240,1266]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Castanea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Castanea</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
